<p>The trailer ends with a number of cryptic shots including a funeral, Michael brandishing a bat in his own home and much more.</p>

<p>The trailer ends with Michael stating, 'I promise you, it's going to be all right.'</p>

<p>The 10-episode series will debut on Showtime in December. </p>

